  "_change_notes": "The fixed proposal after Threshold blocked V18: keeps age 25->18 (the intended change), reverts the frequency cap, and KEEPS r4 as include_is_not_in so missing-cc_bin sessions stay excluded. Decisions change (more under-25 premium buyers become eligible) with no constraint violations -> ELIGIBLE_FOR_HOLDOUT."
